'''卡梅尔'''（{{lang-en|Carmel}}）是位于[[美国|美国]][[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]][[漢密爾頓縣_(印地安納州)|漢密爾頓縣]]的城市，為州府[[印第安纳波利斯|印第安纳波利斯]]北側的衛星城市。卡梅爾以「美國的圓環首都」（Roundabout Capital of the U.S.）知名，因其擁有美國城市中最多的圓環（截至2019年一月共有122座）。

卡梅爾在印第安納波利斯都會區以高教育水準與富裕的地區著稱，每戶平均收入的中位數約為109,201美元、房子平均價格的中位數為320,400美元<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.census.gov/quickfacts/fact/table/carmelcityindiana/PST045217|title=Quick Facts - Carmel city, Indiana|last=|first=|date=|website=U.S. Census Bureau|access-date=January 28, 2019|archive-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404044526/https://www.census.gov/quickfacts/fact/table/carmelcityindiana/PST045217|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡梅爾亦經常受到許多財經雜誌或網站評比為「全美最佳居住地」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://money.com/money/collection/2018-best-places-to-live/5361441/carmel-indiana-2/|title=Carmel, Indiana Is No. 3 on MONEY's Best Places to Live list|website=Money|access-date=2019-01-28|archive-date=2019-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128082819/http://money.com/money/collection/2018-best-places-to-live/5361441/carmel-indiana-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、最安全城市之一、以及最佳開啟職涯與照顧家庭的地點<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.carmel.in.gov/about-the-city/city-wide-awards|title=City Wide Awards {{!}} City of Carmel|website=www.carmel.in.gov|access-date=2019-01-28|archive-date=2019-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128030618/http://www.carmel.in.gov/about-the-city/city-wide-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在某些社交圈中，更將卡梅爾市稱為「中西部的比佛利山莊」<ref>Natalia E. Contreras, [https://www.indystar.com/story/news/local/hamilton-county/carmel/2019/06/30/flipping-exes-new-bravo-tv-show-feature-carmel-ind-couple/1582757001/ "It's the Beverly Hills of the Midwest': Carmel exes flip homes in new reality TV show,"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.indystar.com/story/news/local/hamilton-county/carmel/2019/06/30/flipping-exes-new-bravo-tv-show-feature-carmel-ind-couple/1582757001/ |date=20191224180100 }} ''[[印第安纳波利斯星报|印第安纳波利斯星报]]'', June 30, 2019.</ref>。

==歷史==
卡梅爾一開始被稱為「Bethlehem」，由Daniel Warren、Alexander Mills、John Phelps、Seth Green在1837年建城<ref name=Haines>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z8wWAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA241#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=History of Hamilton County, Indiana: Her People, Industries and Institutions, Volume 1 | publisher=B.F. Bowen & Co. | author=Haines, John F. | year=1915 | access-date=2019-11-15 | archive-date=2020-07-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727181437/https://books.google.com/books?id=Z8wWAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA241#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。城市於1874年更名為卡梅爾市，沿用至今<ref name=Haines/>{{rp|247}}。

1924年，美國最先的交通號誌之一設置於卡梅爾市Main Street與Rangeline Road的交叉口<ref>{{cite web | title=History of Carmel, Indiana | publisher=City of Carmel, Indiana | url=http://www.ci.carmel.in.us/government/History%20of%20Carmel.html | accessdate=2007-03-16 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070615120332/http://www.ci.carmel.in.us/government/History%20of%20Carmel.html | archivedate=2007-06-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==
卡梅爾位於漢密爾頓縣南側，與[[印第安納波利斯|印第安納波利斯]]相接。

==獎項==
卡梅爾市受到以下許多單位或網站授予榮譽或獎項：
*2018年財經雜誌評選為最佳開啟職涯的城市第一名<ref>{{cite news | url=http://time.com/money/5186414/best-places-to-live-start-career/ | work=Time | title=These Are the Best Places in the U.S. to Launch a Career | date=12 March 2018 | accessdate=2019-11-15 | archive-date=2019-01-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108063023/http://time.com/money/5186414/best-places-to-live-start-career/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
*2017、2018年Niche公司評選為全美最佳居住地第一名<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.niche.com/places-to-live/rankings/places/best-places-to-live/|title=2017 Best Places to Live in America|work=Niche|access-date=2017-05-03|archive-date=2017-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170506185549/https://www.niche.com/places-to-live/rankings/places/best-places-to-live/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.niche.com/places-to-live/search/best-places-to-live/|title=2018 Best Places to Live in America|website=Niche|accessdate=2019-11-15|archive-date=2019-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114141108/https://www.niche.com/places-to-live/search/best-places-to-live/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*2017年財經雜誌評選為全美最佳居住地第16名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/money/collection/best-places-to-live-2017/4924328/carmel-indiana/|title=Carmel, Indiana is MONEY's No. 16 Best Place to Live in America|website=Money|accessdate=2019-11-15|archive-date=2018-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181125025954/http://time.com/money/collection/best-places-to-live-2017/4924328/carmel-indiana/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
*2014年財經雜誌評選為全美最佳居住地第三名<ref>{{cite news | url=http://time.com/money/3312311/carmel-indiana-best-places-to-live/ | work=Time | title=Carmel, Ind. is No. 3! See if your town made the list of MONEY's Best Places to Live | date=19 September 2014 | accessdate=2019-11-15 | archive-date=2018-12-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230045939/http://time.com/money/3312311/carmel-indiana-best-places-to-live/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
*2012年CNN財經雜誌評選為全美最佳居住地第一名<ref name="Best Places to Live 2012">{{cite news|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/moneymag/bplive/2012/top100/|title=Best Places to Live 2012|work=CNN}}{{dead link|date=June 2016|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>。
*2002年獲得林業管理最高獎項-金葉獎（Gold Leaf Award）<ref>{{cite web|title=City of Carmel Urban Forestry Awards and Grants|url=http://www.carmel.in.gov/modules/showdocument.aspx?documentid=13|accessdate=20 August 2014|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707154537/http://www.carmel.in.gov/modules/showdocument.aspx?documentid=13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*2006年時任市長Jim Brainard獲得「城市可居住性獎」（City Livability Award），因其於卡梅爾廣設圓環，增進民眾生活品質<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ci.carmel.in.us/government/newsrelease/07-14-06c.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060923112501/http://www.ci.carmel.in.us/government/newsrelease/07-14-06c.htm|archivedate=2006-09-23|title=City of Carmel Receives 2006 City Livability Award for Roundabouts|accessdate=2019-11-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

